universum.studios.android.fragment.annotation.handler

Interface FragmentFactoryAnnotationHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotationHandler

    public interface FragmentFactoryAnnotationHandler
extends AnnotationHandler
    An AnnotationHandler extended interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from BaseFragmentFactory class provided by this library.
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky

      • getFragmentItems

        @Nullable
SparseArray<FragmentItem> getFragmentItems()
        Returns an array with FragmentItems mapped to theirs ids that has been created from @FactoryFragment or @FactoryFragments annotations (if presented).
        Returns:
        Array with fragment items created from the processed annotations or null if there were no annotations specified.
